title: Picture's Up!
description: On a film set, when the AD call's "Rehearsal's Up" it signals that it is time for rehearsal to begin, and when he/she calls "Picture's Up" it signals that rehearsal is over and it is time to begin filming. This podcast is about transitioning from interest in a career in film, to having a career in film.
author: David George

title: TERMINAL
description: TERMINAL ACCESS: GRANTED. Each installment is a carefully curated mixtape of house and techno music, from deep progressive grooves to dark tech house and angry, pounding techno, all mixed live by Bluescreen.
author: Bluescreen
